<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/25845606/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            何为道德的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6729657">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6729657/" class="title-link">藉此潜入思辨的乐境</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6729657"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/50677266/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50677266-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/50677266/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">冯晓春</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-07-07"
      class="main-meta">2014-07-07 11:03:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6729657_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  德国人长于思辨，对形而上的思考传统上是习于浸淫其中乐而忘返，因此多数哲学著作在一般人看来往往晦涩艰深，难以令读者亲近。但是对于有志于独立思考的学人们来说，这本小书对所谓“根本问题”的抽丝剥茧追根究底的阐释，却能给沉下心来慢慢体味阅读求解之乐的他们带来颇具震...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6729657_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6729657_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
